Rajkummar Rao Talks About His Support System And More

metadata.description: The talented Taapsee Pannu is on the cover of Filmfare’s July 2022 issue. Taapsee has essayed the role of Mithali Raj, one of the best women cricketers ever in Shabaash Mithu. She’s been known to play empowered women on screen and talks about that and more in  a heartfelt interview. Catch up with Rajkummar Rao and Bobby Deol as well.
